description: Baby Namer will randomly give you a name from a list of over 33,000 names in the US Social Security Database for the most recent year.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Baby Namer for a baby name
Alexa, ask Baby Namer to name my baby
Alexa, ask Baby Namer for a boy's name
name: Baby Namer
shortDescription: Provides random names from a list of over 33,000 names given to children in the United States.
